name: CliKintoneTest-15 Should return the error message when the API token is incorrect
fullName: features/common.feature#CliKintoneTest-15 Should return the error message when the API token is incorrect

steps.name: When I run the command with args "record export --base-url $$TEST_KINTONE_BASE_URL --app 1 --api-token abc"
Then I should get the exit code is non-zero
And The output error message should match with the pattern: "\[400\] \[GAIA_IA02\] The specified API token does not match the API token generated via an app."

labels.name: suite
labels.value: CliKintoneTest-15 Should return the error message when the API token is incorrect
